      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by. I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. I\u2019ve treated this car like a member of the family\u2014always garaged, hand-washed every Sunday, and kept in absolutely stunning shape. It drives like a dream and looks just as good as the day it rolled off the lot. There might be a microscopic speck from the road if you squint hard enough, but honestly, you won't find one cleaner in the neighborhood. Come by, let's grab a coffee and I'll show you around it!",
