    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a turn-key masterpiece for the discerning driver. This unit features a high-compression powerplant with a perfectly linear torque curve, delivering visceral throttle response that modern forced-induction setups fail to replicate. The chassis has been optimized for maximum rigidity, paired with a precision-tuned limited-slip differential for flawless power delivery through the apex. Meticulously maintained with high-temp synthetic lubricants and shortened service intervals to ensure peak thermal efficiency. The valvetrain remains whisper-quiet with zero parasitic loss, and the close-ratio gearbox offers crisp, positive engagement. This is a mechanically optimized specimen, preserved in showroom condition for the purist who demands peak performance.",
