      "description": "Imagine yourself behind the wheel of a masterpiece that defies the passage of time. This isn't just a vehicle; it's a preserved moment of automotive perfection. Bathed in a finish that glows like liquid midnight, every curve reflects the world with crystalline clarity. Inside, the cabin welcomes you with the intoxicating aroma of untouched leather and the silent promise of a journey unlike any other. Every switch clicks with the satisfying weight of a Swiss watch, and the engine purrs with a symphony of precision that suggests it has been cherished in a climate-controlled sanctuary rather than a mere garage. To drive this car is to command a legacy of elegance and power, a rare opportunity to own a specimen that remains as breathtaking as the day it first graced the showroom floor. It is, quite simply, the pinnacle of its kind.",
      "price": 48950.0,
