      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! It truly breaks my heart to let this beauty go, but it's time for her to find a new home. I\u2019ve treated this car like a member of the family, keeping her tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washing her every single weekend. She honestly looks and drives like she just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014the paint has that deep, mirror-like shine and the interior still has that fresh scent. There's one tiny, microscopic mark near the door handle that you'd probably never notice, but I like to be upfront! If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved with a passion, this is the one. Come on over, let\u2019s talk cars, and you can see for yourself why I\u2019m so proud of her!",
